high_descs: Turn right and look at the counter
Grab the potato off of the counter
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the potato in the microwave and then take it out
Put the potato on the black table
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot potato on the black table

high_descs: Turn to the counter to your right.
Pick up the potato to the right of the plate.
Turn around and go to the microwave, to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the potato in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the potato from the microwave.
Move over to the left side of the table the microwave is o.
Place the potato on the left side of the table, in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato on the microwave stand.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn around and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, heat it up, then take it out.
Moved to the left to face the counter beneath the microwave.
Place the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato on the counter.
